node.text: Go behind the scenes with the 31 “Everyday Smilers” whose grins are the stars of our newest campaign benefiting Operation Smile – and then grab a Lay’s Smiles bag to learn more about the great work they’re doing in communities nationwide.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lay's on August 25, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, body of water and text that says 'Lays Salt Vinegar'.

node.text: Lay's outside just hit different ya know? #LetsSummer

node.text: Are you Team Doritos or Team Funyuns? Tell us and we may send you that chip to try!

node.text: We’re taking it global again with a British classic 🇬🇧 and a Colombian staple 🇨🇴. Who you got in this round of our INTERNATIONAL FLAVOR FACE-OFF?
